Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.51,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Now that's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:57.62,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. My key to victory is Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:02.00,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get in contact with Gojo Satoru\Nby any means necessary,
