Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:05.96,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}and have him rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.13,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}As much as I would like to focus on Geto,\N the one who deployed this Veil,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.22,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mahito is too dangerous to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.72,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to exorcise him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.56,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,One-Year Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.19,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Incinerate, Mechamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.69,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Ultra Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.59,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Gonna keep incinerating me until \NI'm out of cursed energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:59.77,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Then I'll have to drag you outta there!
