Comment: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:35.03,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:44.87,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mechamaru's attacks won't be enough\N to damage Mahito's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.92,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's well aware of it now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.50,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Two-Year Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.17,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Miracle Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.93,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know you won't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.15,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're underestimating my attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:55.11,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,It's about time you get a taste of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.45,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is he so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:06.08,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,If this drags on for too long, he'll destroy my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.83,Default,System Voice,0,0,0,,Technique loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:14.09,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,I've only got four chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:19.34,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,I'll end this in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.56,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Fire, Mechamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.48,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You thought that would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.57,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Guess you haven't seen enough, then. {in response to his "I have seen it all." line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.07,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Wait{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.22,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.93,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even my soul was destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.11,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.49,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Bird again? You've got zero creativity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.33,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}The left arm I blew away has regenerated already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:33.62,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, he's just manipulating the shape of his soul\N to make it look like it regenerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.67,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that he's showing it off makes it obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.63,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.76,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}My plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.76,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.56,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,He's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:55.35,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It might be temporary, but his cursed energy\N output is on par with a special-grade's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.52,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,He came prepared to deal with Mahito, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.28,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,At this rate, he might just... {Depending on how this goes, this could be the moment...} {what the absolute fuck did cr mean by this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.91,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Five-Year Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.04,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Pigeon Viola!
Comment: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.78,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.22,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell which of his attacks affect my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:10.01,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's start with figuring that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.45,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.20,Default,System Voice,0,0,0,,Technique loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.12,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.50,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be together with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.10,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Domain Expansion:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.06,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Self-Embodiment of Perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.46,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,And we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.81,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Idle Transfiguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:50.15,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if I'm touching you directly\N once you're inside my domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:53.11,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,But you already knew that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:02.21,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}These contain a special technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:07.75,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the only way I could make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.59,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,There's only ten days until Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:15.34,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Did you assume I won't use my domain\Nto conserve cursed energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:18.06,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Ten days is more than enough\N for a full recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.73,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've only got two left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.36,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}This technique is from the Heian Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:32.74,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the Golden Age of Sorcery, when cursed spirits\N and curse users were running rampant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.95,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashiya Sadatsuna devised this to protect his disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Don't bring hopes and dreams into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.25,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,It's so pathetic I don't even know how to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.88,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was passed down through the generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:53.01,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}Revealing it to outsiders was forbidden by a Binding Vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.09,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a technique that lets you\N protect yourself from others' domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.94,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}The domain for the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.86,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.53,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,New Shadow Style: Simple Domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.75,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have seen it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:51.23,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Simple Domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.99,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\i1}A domain neutralizes any deployed techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:58.99,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attacks inside a domain will always hit,\N even on Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:04.24,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may be a simple one,\N but if a domain is activated from the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.87,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\i1}then even Mahito will take damage, \Nregardless of his technique. {in a recent chapter (246) gege said simple_domain doesn't neutralize techniques, and geto never used that specific word either so im changing this line, but the question still remains: what exactly happened here?} {does SD have a sure-hit effect? even if that was the case, the problem was never that the attacks didn't hit, it was that any damage they did was reverted by mahito reinforcing the shape of his soul, so i don't see any way of damaging mahito short of neutralizing his technique} {maybe there's some hint in how other characters manage to harm him}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:17.17,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Enough spectating from the sidelines,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.05,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Geto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.48,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a fortunate miscalculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:30.02,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still have one Simple Domain\N and nine years of cursed energy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.56,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can fight Geto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.07,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:41.78,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can be together with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.38,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed to finish him off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.26,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Come, Mechamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.48,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still have one domain left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.48,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll ram it directly into him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.82,Default,Muta,0,0,0,,Let's do this, Mechamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.34,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Hey, Mechamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.51,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,You think I can come visit you sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:28.56,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Ever since that baseball game at the exchange event,\N I feel like we've all gotten a lot closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.06,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just part of being a sorcerer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:36.19,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,but we used to keep our distance \Neven though we got along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:42.44,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Losing someone close is all the more painful, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:48.33,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,But you know what? I really like how we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.70,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,Remember how you couldn't participate\N in the baseball game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.46,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,We got a pitching machine to fill in for you! {wait i thought he literally was the pitching machine... but huh this makes sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:03.63,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,I'd like to get closer to you as well, Mechamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:11.01,Default,Miwa,0,0,0,,So, one day, I'll come see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.81,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Cutting it a little close, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:21.32,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,As soon as he activated his technique,\N I made myself burst apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.82,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Then I deactivated my domain to fake my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.07,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,It was all calculated. Nothing close about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.20,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Simple Domain could be used like that, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.58,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Good thing we got to see it in action\N before the main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.08,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.50,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I also finished tweaking the conditions\N of the commissioned Veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.88,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Now we should be able to have someone else\N perform the activation procedure. {he actually mentions "cursed energy and chant" which is required to activate the veil, but it makes things confusing and it's all part of the activation procedure anyway}
